 144:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****      flushes the fifo :
 145:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****      (+) In polling mode, the output of the function is done when the transfer
 146:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_xspi.c ****          complete bit is set and the busy bit cleared.
